column5: Decided to take the boat out and try for some lakersLaunching was ok but w√†ter is very shallow as you get out of prop wash hole.Went 3/4 of a mile and ran into ice.pretty black and i could bust it but hit solid ice also.Mhhhh thought it would of been gone.Tried trolling the where i had open water and did not catch anything.Was nice to get out and check boat out.Guess ill try again in a few more days.
